    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. but some people argue that the whole system is actually outdated and just protects the interests of the big powers instead of being a real neutral body. do historians see those kinds of criticisms as valid or is that more of a fringe view?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
